sections.text:
44-5416.Utilization Review Act, how cited.

Sections 44-5416 to 44-5431 shall be known and may be cited as the Utilization Review Act.

SourceLaws 1992, LB 428, § 1;R.S.1943, (1993), § 44-5401;Laws 1998, LB 1162, § 1.
